rows.label: qst001803_msg0001
rows.name: Romney... You're safe. I'm so glad...

rows.label: qst001803_msg0002
rows.name: Sorry for worrying you...

rows.label: qst001803_msg0003
rows.name:
Indeed. You need to get stronger
so I don't have to worry, Romney.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0004
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]No, that's enough of that!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0005
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]You understand now, don't you?

rows.label: qst001803_msg0006
rows.name: I'm still too young to be a Driver.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I have to get stronger, like these
guys, before I can go on a journey!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]But you won't get stronger unless
you go on a journey, will you?

rows.label: qst001803_msg0009
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]There's a limit to that!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0010
rows.name:
I should learn the basics of the
sword and be able to fight properly
before I go on a journey!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0011
rows.name:
You're doing everything
backwards, Olua!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0012
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]It's like you're trying to make
me a great chef when I don't
even know how to hold a knife.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0013
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]You'll get the hang of it if
you just get used to it!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0014
rows.name: Everyone is a beginner at first!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0015
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Ah...

rows.label: qst001803_msg0016
rows.name:
Let's talk about this later. We
need to thank these people first.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0017
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I don't care about that!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0018
rows.name:
I'm going home! You can do your
training journey by yourself, Olua!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Wait, Romney!

rows.label: qst001803_msg0020
rows.name:
Everyone, this is for you.
If we meet again somewhere,
let's talk then.

rows.label: qst001803_msg0021
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]A lover's quarrel is something
even a Nopon can't stomach...
